vyges-lvs compares two SPICE netlists (a layout-extracted netlist vs the
schematic/reference) for structural equivalence — device and net matching by
name-independent graph refinement — and reports where they diverge.

Per-foundry device-recognition / extraction decks, where applicable, are
distributed separately under their own terms and are not part of this repository.
